org.paces.Stata.Variables

Class DataColumn

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.paces.Stata.Variables.DataColumn

  • public class DataColumn
extends Object
    Class to return all values of a single Stata variable. This class requires the detection of the Stata variable types.

    0.0.0
    Author:
    Billy Buchanan
